{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/multiplefontsizesemantictokens"]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Kind of semantic tokens which will wrap a combination of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/FontSizeSemanticToken","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" depending to size classes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Allows to gather the multiple-value tokens from Figma inside one object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If a font size exists with its value depending to the size class, it must be packed in such "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/init(_:)","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/init(compact:regular:)"],"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/compact","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/regular"],"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/isEqual(_:)"],"title":"Instance Methods","anchor":"Instance-Methods"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"final"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text"